{
  "stem": "7600.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really think I walked around dirty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was just so hard to do anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the apartment was horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother had sold all of her beautiful stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the relatives, I mean, we could-- when we visited relatives, they would give us cookies or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Only my Uncle Julius, the one that was also a dentist, he would sometimes give us a little money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But all the others, they just gave us a little cookies or cake or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't do anything for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we couldn't talk to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To me, they were like ancient, in their 60s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was the life in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I hated it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I couldn't wait till my father found some place where we could go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then, in 1937, he talked to somebody, and he found out there was another brother my grandmother had, who was like the black sheep of the family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he came to the United States at the turn of the century, maybe 1903 or 1905 or maybe 1900.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he left Austria in that days, and he came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In those days, in the early 1900s, if somebody did something in the family, they used to send them to United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the thing to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The bad people used to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They did something, so there, this is where you put all of the rejects.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they must have sent him there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we found out he had a wife and he had-- that he was also-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and he had three sons.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he found out he had-- well, we'll to go to the United States, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
